'''飓风阿琳'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Arlene}}）是1987年大西洋飓风季持续时间最长的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是该季第一场飓风和首场获命名的风暴。系统源自[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]海岸沿线逐渐衰减的[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统]]所关联的[[低气压|低气压区]]，成型后总体保持向东移动，逐渐穿越[[大西洋|大西洋]]，期间多次大幅转向。8月13日，气旋以弱热带风暴强度掠过[[百慕大|百慕大]]，然后继续在海上前进。8月20日，阿琳一度停止移动，再于两天后升级成飓风。8月24日清晨，风暴在北大西洋极北洋面上空转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，然后回转东南，于8月26日在[[伊比利亚半岛|伊比利亚半岛]]附近逐渐消散。

阿琳在百慕大产生时速93公里的强风和3.7米的大浪，该岛遭受的破坏程度很轻。此时正有一位盲人在海上驾船前行，希望能成为史上首位独自穿越大西洋的盲人，飓风引起的恶劣海况和狂风在前后两天内对他的船造成价值8000美元的破坏。8月26至27日间，气旋残留还在[[西欧|西欧]]多地降下暴雨。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Arlene 1987 track.png}}
飓风阿琳源自8月8日[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]海岸沿线逐渐衰减的[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统]]所关联的[[低气压|低气压区]]。系统向东南方向前进，移动路线形成[[反气旋|反气旋]]环路，在此期间其组织结构缓慢改善，强度也慢慢提高。到了8月10日，低气压区已逼近[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]，但依然杂乱无章。次日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]根据卫星图像将位于[[安德罗斯岛|安德罗斯岛]]上空的天气系统归类成1987年大西洋飓风季第三号热带低气压。<ref name="PG1">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180027/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim01.gif | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 1987-10-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report: Page One | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>

受逐渐逼近[[美国东部|美国东部]]的[[低压槽|低压槽]]和南侧一条拉长的[[亚热带气旋|副热带]][[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，系统在成为热带气旋后转向西北<ref name="PG1" />，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月11日下午18点增强成热带风暴<ref name="hurdat">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Specialists Unit | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2011 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Atlantic Best Tracks, 1851 to 2010 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205507/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2011.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2011.html }}</ref>。但是，气象机构直至[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机测得飞行高度层风速达到每小时80公里后才将气旋升级。阿琳接下来沿[[大西洋|大西洋]]上空的低压槽边缘朝[[百慕大|百慕大]]前进<ref name="PG1" />。

8月13日，阿琳因附近低压槽的制约而无法得到显著发展。{{lang|en|UTC}}下午15点左右，气旋中心从百慕大以北约89公里海域经过。数小时后，有船只在风暴中心附近测得时速121公里的狂风，但由于阿琳此时层次依然混乱，气象机构认为这样高的风速并不能代表气旋的真实强度。接下来几天里，阿琳从多个低气压系统边缘经过。<ref name="PG1" />8月15日，风暴已转朝东南方向移动，再于8月18日转向东北。在此期间，气旋强度继续波动，风速最低时降至每小时64公里，最高时则达到每小时105公里。<ref name="hurdat" />

[[File:Hurricane_Arlene_(1987).JPG|thumb]]存在，风暴也在这天增强成飓风。]]

风暴继续朝东北前进，移动速度在8月18日经过[[短波_(气象学)|短波槽]]后加快<ref name="MWR">{{cite journal | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | author1 = Robert A. Case | author2 = Harold P. Gerrish | journal = Monthly Weather Review | publisher = American Meteorological Society | date = 1988-04 | volume = 116 | issue = 4 | pages = 939–949 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1987 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040405/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1988)116<0939:AHSO>2.0.CO;2 | format = PDF | bibcode = 1988MWRv..116..939C | access-date = 2016-05-31 }}</ref>。8月20日，阿琳周围的转向气流瓦解，气旋接下来24小时几乎停止移动<ref name="PG1" />。风暴在这段时间发展出良好的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]，强度也相应提升<ref name="MWR" />。随着卫星图像上出现[[风眼|眼状特征]]，美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月20日晚22点将阿琳升级成飓风。但经风暴过后的重新分析该机构又认定，气旋实际上直到{{lang|en|UTC}}8月22日早上6点才达到飓风标准。<ref name="PG2">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-10-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report: Page Two | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim02.gif | location = Miami, FL | format = GIF | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230649/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim02.gif | dead-url = no }}</ref>此时距系统最初成为热带气旋已经过了14.5天<ref name="hurdat" />。

成为飓风后，阿琳因[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]附近逐渐增强的[[高气压|高气压区]]影响而快速北上<ref name="PG2" />。不久后，气旋达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]121公里，最低[[气压|气压]]987[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.15[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="hurdat" />。风暴继续急速北上，开始因北太平洋寒冷洋面上空的[[锋_(气象)|斜压区]]影响而逐渐朝[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]转变，转变过程于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月24日凌晨0点完成。阿琳的温带残留继续沿高气压天气系统边缘行进，于次日转向东南。到8月26日时，系统的结构已经越来越混乱，难以在卫星图像上准确定位，最终于{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点在[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]近海消散。<ref name="PG2" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Remnants_of_Hurricane_Arlene_1987_near_Spain.jpg|thumb]]附近。]]
热带风暴阿琳逼近百慕大之际，有关部门建议岛上居民注意防范，加固住房，气象部门之后很快向岛上发布热带风暴公告<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''Miami Herald'' | date = 1987-08-13 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Bermuda boards up for Arlene | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367CA760B4795&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120094249/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367CA760B4795&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。8月12日，百慕大全岛因气旋的[[雨带|外围雨带]]影响出现狂风天气<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]'' | date = 1987-08-12 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Storm Arlene Launches Hurricane Season | archivedate = 2016-04-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160410065743/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1337451.html | deadurl = yes | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1337451.html | via = HighBeam Research }}</ref>。风暴在岛上产生的最高降雨量为42毫米<ref name="WPCMAX">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M. | date = 2015-04-29 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | chapter-url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120194350/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | publisher = United States Weather Prediction Center | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Point Maxima | archivedate = 2016-01-20 }}</ref>。此时有一位盲人正在海上驾船前行，希望能成为史上首位独自穿越大西洋的盲人。8月14日，他的船在海上遭遇风暴正面袭击，全长11米的“大开眼界号”[[单桅纵帆船|单桅纵帆船]]受到3.7米大浪和时速97公里大风的冲击，迫使他赶往百慕大港口躲避<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''The Washington Post'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307202336/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1337995.html | deadurl = yes | date = 1987-08-15 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Blind Sailor Arrives Safely In Bermuda; D.C. Man Rode Out Storm for Two Days | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1337995.html | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | via = HighBeam Research }}</ref>，船体也因气旋受到价值约8000美元的破坏<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''The Washington Post'' | date = 1987-08-14 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Sailor Riding Out Storm; Blind Washingtonian Heading for Bermuda | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1337902.html | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307143508/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1337902.html | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。8月14日，阿琳从百慕大近海掠过，岛上降下瓢泼大雨，还受到时速93公里的阵风和3.7米的大浪冲击。不过风暴中心自始至终远离海岸，所以岛上遭受的破坏程度很轻。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''Miami Herald'' | date = 1987-08-14 | accessdate = 2016-05-31 | title = Arlene passes Bermuda | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367CBAE086528&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120094351/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367CBAE086528&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>8月26日，阿琳的温带残留对西班牙产生影响，[[罗塔_(加的斯省)|罗塔]]降下32毫米雨量，打破1971年创下的8月降雨量最高纪录<ref name="PG2" />。气旋的残留湿气继续经过[[地中海|地中海]]，再于8月27日令[[意大利|意大利]]普降暴雨<ref>{{cite news | author1 = J.G. Pinto | author2 = M. Klawa | author3 = U. Ulbrich | author4 = R. .Rudari | author5 = P. Speth | publisher = Centro di Ricerca Interuniversitario in Monitoraggio Ambientale | date = 2001-10 | accessdate = 2011-10-05 | title = Extreme Precipitation Events Over Northwest Italy | url = http://www.meteo.uni-koeln.de/content/downloads/Pinto_et_al2001_Plinius.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111005055448/http://www.meteo.uni-koeln.de/content/downloads/Pinto_et_al2001_Plinius.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-10-05 }}</ref>。

